        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This staff of magically hardened wood is topped with a silver sculpture depicting magical runic symbols. When used as a weapon, a staff of power is a +2 greater striking staff.</p>\n<p>Voluntarily destroying a staff of power unleashes an incredible blast of energy. When wielding the staff, you can Interact to break it. This releases a 30-foot-burst magical explosion centered on the staff. This deals [[/r 2d8]] force damage per charge remaining in the staff (DC 40 basic Reflex save). You automatically critically fail your save. A creature reduced to 0 Hit Points by this damage dies instantly; this is a death effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Ray of Enfeeblement]{Ray of Enfeeblement}</li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Continual Flame]{Continual Flame}</li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Levitate]{Levitate}</li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Globe of Invulnerability]{Globe of Invulnerability}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Paralyze]{Paralyze}</li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Magic Missile]{Magic Missile}</li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Wall of Force]{Wall of Force}</li>\n<li><strong>7th</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Cone of Cold]{Cone of Cold}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Fireball]{Fireball}, @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Lightning Bolt]{Lightning Bolt}</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
